The result is approximately \( 9.13286 \times 10^{-35}  \text{J s} \). Rounded to three significant figures, this is \( 9.13 \times 10^{-35}  \text{J s} \). Since the unit for the answer is \( 10^{-35}  \text{J s} \), the numerical value is 9.13.

